     * 4. Wait past CE1, Withdraw 3 ETH -> S=7,  C=0, P=0, CE=0 (Withdraw moves C->P then clears P, resets CE)
     * 5. Stake 2 ETH          -> S=9,  C=0, P=0, CE=0
     * 6. Unstake 4 ETH        -> S=5,  C=4, P=0, CE=T'+cd (cooldownEnd2)
