     * 8. Withdraw 4 ETH       -> S=5,  C=0, P=0, CE=0 (Withdraw checks C, moves C->P, clears P, resets CE)
     * 9. Stake 4 ETH          -> S=9,  C=0, P=0, CE=0
     * 10. Unstake 4 ETH       -> S=5,  C=4, P=0, CE=T''+cd (cooldownEnd3)
